title: i have a mission that is impossible for me to finish.
body: i have completed all the worlds missions except one, which is to finish 4 worlds missions. IDK  how that is possible unless more missions are coming out soon.

replies.body: ok good, i was worried for a second.
More missions are indeed coming as Worlds progresses. Be on the lookout for those missions later on in the week.
More missions will be coming out soon. Just wait!
